
Release history for Jojo-Base

0.7.0     2018-08-21 12:34:02-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Use public Jojo::Role->make_role() method
    - Require Jojo::Role 0.5.0+

v0.6     2017-11-11 10:45:46-08:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Require Mojolicious 7.43+

v0.5     2017-11-08 10:53:07-08:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Export a dummy "with" when role support is missing
    - Depend on Jojo::Role 0.4.0+
    - Fix "with" from "-base" or "-role"

v0.4.1     2017-11-07 16:19:26-08:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Depend on "experimental" (core after v5.19.1)

v0.4     2017-11-07 16:12:23-08:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Use Jojo::Role 0.3.0+ for role support (including shorthands)
    - Automatically enable "lexical_subs" feature
    - Upgrade feature bundle from 5.10 to 5.18
    - Rename Mojo::Bass to Jojo::Base
    - Use Jojo::Role 0.2.0+ for role support
    - Use %EXPORT_TAGS and %EXPORT_GEN for generating exports

v0.3     2017-11-06 18:40:25-08:00 America/Los_Angeles (TRIAL RELEASE)

    - Export "with" when using "-base"
    - Added -role flag to Mojo::Bass

v0.2     2017-11-03 14:27:39-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Added -signatures flag to Mojo::Bass

v0.1.1   2017-10-01 12:31:00-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Fix packaging issue

v0.1     2017-10-01 12:18:06-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Initial version
